lenders.name: Trade Wind Statues
lenders.loan_because: We believe in paying it forward!  By creating opportunity for entrepreneurs throughout the world we can strengthen diversity and resilience in the global economy.  By focusing on loans to women we are striving towards sustainability by creating opportunity.  These opportunities address some of our most pressing global concerns, namely: human rights, poverty, population, access to health care and education, and natural resource conservation. Every success that we have in our business is passed along or "paid forward" by supporting and providing loans to women entrepreneurs in developing countries.
lenders.occupational_info:
At Trade Wind Statues™ it is our goal to bring about positive change in people’s lives.  We are achieving this goal by providing people with magnificent statues, statues that not only add something special to any space, but statues that are also bridging cultural and economic gaps. 

    Trade Wind Statues™ is unique in that we work directly with many of the artisans and people within the communities where we purchase our statues in an effort to promote the principles of sustainability and Fair Trade, while at the same time ensuring that our statues are of the highest quality available.  We work with our customers to assist them in purchasing a statue which will represent something meaningful in their lives.

    We are able to bring our customers statues that are of an extremely rare size and quality in the United States, therefore, we offer our customers something that is as extraordinary as the individual purchasing it, and as exceptional as the one who created it.
